{"tid":2113103,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美軍再次在南海舉行雙航母演習   今個月的第二次","createTime":"2020-07-18T01:33:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T01:44:11.000Z","uid":79563,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c2d0606bc3c5f2e644bc42c11c20f3711fb20ace","tid":2113103,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T01:33:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538478-20200718.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538478-20200718.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiSL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=41341d35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538478-20200718.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9a9ff5a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538478-20200718.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美軍再次在南海舉行雙航母演習，是今個月的第二次。<br />\n<br />\n美軍太平洋艦隊發表聲明，指「列根號」及「尼米茲號」航母戰鬥群，星期五在南海演練，強調不是為了回應任何特定政治或全球事件，而是定期聯合演習。<br />\n<br />\n「尼米茲號」的指揮官說，他們會在國際法容許的範圍內活動，加強對維持印太自由開放、以規則為基礎的國際秩序，以及對區內盟友的承諾。"},{"pid":"171e6f2bd0db0ec4fadb06633de60968b9f28ec1","tid":2113103,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T01:41:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227a2a9fb799945b5a6e41e75cdf69c9351594ce","tid":2113103,"uid":23635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T01:44:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cae32a78b22b39df5d231446990a